This file describes changes in recent versions of cerebro. It
primarily documents those changes that are of interest to users and
admins.

Changes in cerebro-1.2-1
===========================
 -- Documentation updates

Changes in cerebro-1.1-1
===========================
 -- Allow cerebro to work on multiple subnets.
 -- Added load average, memory, and network traffic metric modules.
 -- Support event based monitoring.
 -- Various bug fixes.

Changes in cerebro-1.0-4
===========================
 -- Added graceful shutdown metric module.
 -- Allow monitor modules to support multiple metrics.
 -- Various bug fixes.

Changes in cerebro-1.0-1
===========================
 -- Initial Release

